dBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"黃+藍變綠<br />\n柒婆唔理市民生死，係民居附近設立大型隔離營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"【唔洗搶啦】未買到口罩嘅手足入一入嚟 btw 1.29 全城罷工 封城自治 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNJCqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNJCqS</a>"},{"pid":"ce9f2a1770cc6c8f78693e4a8ba151648ed10339","tid":1843681,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dd9fa23a81f215df053d50a4e9791b62959c3e","tid":1843681,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe89e52e44846ab913513b52ac69afcf4066e1f","tid":1843681,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫推！！！光復香港睇今次！！！！！</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[幫推求共識！！！]公投應否主動向藍絲釋出善意 connect哂所有人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be4e89483b266bfda28d49e1e9017dad42c9ea98","tid":1843681,"uid":45131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98dd246078044b7fe7e5e5e8b3472edeff35ecc8","tid":1843681,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"黃+藍變綠<br />\n柒婆唔理市民生死，係民居附近設立大型隔離營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"王＋南我個fd個名泥"},{"pid":"9b00f81bee23f4babfc21bfa590526928b9a8f6b","tid":1843681,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"63e7e2f397c92366f79e7a4229caabcd5516a782","tid":1843681,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"全民司政，用香港地投票app<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Muisco.HKVote&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.Muisco.HKVote%26hl%3Den_US&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=868e854a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Muisco.HKVote&amp;hl=en_US</a>"},{"pid":"9e66fe8beb36c61dc00b59fbf8d7570ab72030db","tid":1843681,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦<br />\n武漢肺炎幾個月內收到佢地皮所以佢地先咁關心<br />\n2047佢地晨早死撚咗點會care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfec449a8d3436d074542867efe42acf407f2fb","tid":1843681,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬到底明唔明所有藍絲都係自私撚，除非波及到佢地，否則佢哋只會無動於衷"},{"pid":"9323743b70128c36bc8ab1959bc791de1aabbabf","tid":1843681,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">請廣傳 </span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=462a0195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡<br />\n整體分析：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=9ccb7dc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n首選：Sellstrom S80225/S80226 Wildland Fire Goggles （戴眼鏡都用得）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB07DJVPL9Q&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6e8012b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Sellstrom-Wildland-Goggles-Non-Vented-Anti-Fog/dp/B07DJVPL9Q</a><br />\n<br />\nSellstrom 依款眼罩，上年九月果陣，已經係前線手足標準裝備，有手足認證，包保放心！其中，依款眼罩有兩大特點。<br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩寫明係 non-vented，即係氣密。戴左之後，基本上就阻隔左外面嘅空氣進入眼罩，所以擋到TG，亦都擋到帶病毒嘅飛沫同空氣，乜春都入唔到眼。依個亦都係佢可以俾美國消防員救山火果陣用嘅原因。氣密係眼罩第一重要條件，如果唔係氣密，病毒同TG都可以經眼罩邊位入眼，大陸衛健委都講明病毒傳染性不斷上升，美國有教授都講左武漢沙士嘅reproductive rate 高過曬佢見過佢嘅病毒，證明今次係非常嚴重，必須要用高規格嘅產品保護自己！<br />\n<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過 ANSI Z87+ 嘅驗證，保護性極高！<br />\nANSI Z87+嘅定義如下：<br />\n&lsquo;Each product must go through rigorous third-party testing which simulates hazards such as impact by flying objects and debris, high mass impact, and sharp object penetration. In each testing scenario, the lenses and frame must stay intact to pass&rsquo;<br />\n根據網上一個對ANSI Z87+ 眼罩嘅測試，散彈槍都射佢唔穿，所以ANSI Z87+ 嘅standard 係非常高，亦都只有依種眼罩嘅保護性先可以保護前線免受橡膠子彈同布袋彈威脅。<br />\n<br />\n次選：Pyramex CAPSTONE (G504DT或其他型號）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog%2Fdp%2FB003UUEW88&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=757b4d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Pyramex-Capstone-Direct-Indirect-Anti-Fog/dp/B003UUEW88</a><br />\n<br />\n第一，依款眼罩有氣密帽，應該同樣做到氣密效果，但係因為佢嘅氣密帽可以拆卸，多左個連接位，所以氣密保護性會低小小（始終多個連接位就多個出錯機會）。<br />\n第二，依款眼罩經過D3 測試，證實可以防水滴同化學劑嘅飛淺，理論上有足夠防水性能。<br />\n第三，依款眼罩經過MIL-PRF 32432 美軍標準測試，對子彈衝擊力有一定防禦。<br />\n<br />\n最後選擇：泳鏡（仲易買過平光鏡）<br />\n<br />\n泳鏡顧名思義，就係for 遊水，氣密效果有一定嘅保證，同埋求其一間運動鋪都可以買到，買近視鏡嘅話眼睛都唔洗戴，幾十蚊就有，保護性一定好過平光鏡，不過如果係講嘢都要除口罩，放屁要除褲，戴左帽可能腦都用唔到嘅人，可能佢戴左就會睇唔野。<br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手，like &amp; share 等多啲人睇到！<br />\n<br />\n#屠龍 #藍絲 #藍屍 #黃色經濟圈 #黃店 #裝備 #口罩 #武漢肺炎 #武漢 #P95 #文宣 #N95 #肺炎 #沙士 #香港 #支那人 #高鐵 #眼罩 #tg #lihkg #連登 #高登 #d100 #黑警"}]}